  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/338070/extras/d0b3fb16a42e5969ce6c6c39a74baccc.avif?t=1716526349\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br><strong>ARTDINK \"Legend Pack\" Series</strong><br><br>The ARTDINK \"Legend Pack\" Series is a compilation of ARTDINK's masterpiece works of the 1980s and 1990s. The PC9800 versions of these games can finally be played in Windows. In addition, a Library Mode exclusive to the \"Legend Pack\" allows you to browse illustrations, graphic and sound data.<br><br>\"Lunatic Dawn Legend Pack\" is a compilation containing the following titles:<br>\"Lunatic Dawn\" (original release 1993)<br>\"Lunatic Dawn II\" (original release 1994)<br>\"Lunatic Dawn III\" (original release 1998)<br><br>Lunatic Dawn are non-linear RPG games set in Medieval Eurasia inspired world.<br><br><strong>This game is only available in Japanese.</strong>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/338070/extras/d0b3fb16a42e5969ce6c6c39a74baccc.avif?t=1716526349\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br><strong>ARTDINK \"Legend Pack\" Series</strong><br><br>The ARTDINK \"Legend Pack\" Series is a compilation of ARTDINK's masterpiece works of the 1980s and 1990s. The PC9800 versions of these games can finally be played in Windows. In addition, a Library Mode exclusive to the \"Legend Pack\" allows you to browse illustrations, graphic and sound data.<br><br>\"Lunatic Dawn Legend Pack\" is a compilation containing the following titles:<br>\"Lunatic Dawn\" (original release 1993)<br>\"Lunatic Dawn II\" (original release 1994)<br>\"Lunatic Dawn III\" (original release 1998)<br><br>Lunatic Dawn are non-linear RPG games set in Medieval Eurasia inspired world.<br><br><strong>This game is only available in Japanese.</strong>",
